{"tid":1949663,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有冇得食日式嘅台灣撈麵? 台湾まぜそば","createTime":"2020-03-29T20:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T03:33:44.000Z","uid":254330,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc007055463e53e962b22a68ce91e95ce89000d","tid":1949663,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:49:17.000Z","msg":"首先唔知佢叫中文名叫咩, 就咁google「台灣撈麵」又出唔到我想要嘅結果, 咁為左方便我打字同埋唔洗同時歧視2個國家, 就叫佢<span style=\"color: red;\">新型撈麵</span>先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前係日本食過次新型撈麵, 鐘意佢上有勁多蔥、蛋、肉燥、芝士, 下面就係彈牙嘅麵 比起飯, 似乎麵更加好食<br />\n<br />\n圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QX2Xx9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQX2Xx9g.jpg&h=3b7ef492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://oceans-nadia.com/user/23165/recipe/374828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foceans-nadia.com%2Fuser%2F23165%2Frecipe%2F374828&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c239f454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://oceans-nadia.com/user/23165/recipe/374828</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣嘅台灣撈麵都食過, 但係覺得冇乜特別<br />\n新型撈麵睇落就係台灣肉燥飯做reference, 再落堆各種唔同新料落去, 而個味又幾啱我食<br />\n係日本每間新型撈麵都有佢嘅feature, 配料都會有唔同, 幾正<br />\n<br />\n依家去唔撚到日本食, 香港有冇得食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle搵到間「富士山55」不過執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>一風堂美心的不了</strong></span>"},{"pid":"70e9b086045c5d511407a16f169c04fa9960236b","tid":1949663,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:58:24.000Z","msg":"想食日本油麵<br />\n撈得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e942bb3ccdc0ad3fea0ce11e9a9799ef1b38fe","tid":1949663,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70e9b086045c5d511407a16f169c04fa9960236b","tid":1949663,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyT